    <criteria>
      <textblock>
        Inclusion Criteria:

          -  Healthy volunteers

          -  Body mass index (BMI) 18.5-25 kg/m2

        Exclusion Criteria:

          -  Systolic blood pressure over 150 mmHg

          -  Any continuous medication (hormonal intrauterine device is permitted)

          -  Any significant medical condition

          -  Insensitivity to rifampicin

